@startuml
actor User as User
participant "Conversation Service\n(NestJS)" as Conv
participant "Conversation DB" as ConvDB
participant "RabbitMQ Broker" as RabbitMQ
participant "Chatbot Service\n(Python)" as Chatbot
participant "Chatbot DB" as ChatbotDB

== User gửi yêu cầu xóa ==
User -> Conv: DELETE /code-conversation-service/chats/:id
activate Conv

== Lưu trạng thái và ghi nhận Outbox ==
Conv -> ConvDB: UPDATE Chat (isActive=false) & INSERT Outbox (ChatDeletedEvent)
activate ConvDB
ConvDB --> Conv: Commit Transaction
deactivate ConvDB

Conv --> User: HTTP 200 OK (Phản hồi thành công ngay lập tức)
deactivate Conv

== Relayer quét Outbox gửi đi ==
note over Conv, RabbitMQ: Cron job OutboxRelay quét DB định kỳ
Conv -> ConvDB: SELECT PENDING OutboxEvents
activate ConvDB
ConvDB --> Conv: Danh sách events
deactivate ConvDB

Conv -> RabbitMQ: Publish 'ChatDeletedEvent' (Queue: chat_deletions)
activate RabbitMQ
RabbitMQ --> Conv: Ack
deactivate RabbitMQ

Conv -> ConvDB: UPDATE Outbox status='DONE'
activate ConvDB
ConvDB --> Conv: OK
deactivate ConvDB

== Chatbot xử lý đồng bộ xóa ==
RabbitMQ --> Chatbot: Consume 'ChatDeletedEvent' (args: chatId, userId)
activate Chatbot

Chatbot -> ChatbotDB: Soft Delete toàn bộ Messages liên quan tới chatId
activate ChatbotDB
ChatbotDB --> Chatbot: OK
deactivate ChatbotDB

Chatbot --> RabbitMQ: Acknowledge (Hoàn tất)
deactivate Chatbot
@enduml
